rsofun P-model GPP and leaf D13C validation data

Source: R/data.R
pmodel_validation.Rd

Small example dataset of target observations (daily GPP flux data as well as leaf D13C data) to optimize model parameters with the function calib_sofun

pmodel_validation

Format

A tibble of validation data:

sitename

A character string containing the site name (e.g. 'FR-Pue').

targets

A single one-row tibble with a column for each target containing TRUE or FALSE (or NA_logical)

data

A single tibble or a list of tibbles with target observations. For daily simulations this single tibble can contain daily values for:

date

Date vector with format YYYY-MM-DD.

gpp

The observed Gross Primary Productivity (GPP) for each time stamp (in gC m\(^{-2}\) d\(^{-1}\)).

gpp_qc

A quality check indicator.

le

Latent heat of exchange ...

...

... etc.

For onestep acclimation this can fore example include:

bigD13C

A tibble containing observations of leaf D13C values.

Vcmax

A tibble containing observations of Vcmax values.

Jmax

A tibble containing observations of Jmax values.

Source

Pastorello, G., Trotta, C., Canfora, E. et al. The FLUXNET2015 dataset and the ONEFlux processing pipeline for eddy covariance data. Sci Data 7, 225 (2020). https://doi.org/10.1038/s41597-020-0534-3

Cornwell, W. (2025). traitecoevo/leaf13C: V0.2.2 (Version v0.2.2) [Computer software]. Zenodo. https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.15239220

Cornwell, William K., et al. “Climate and soils together regulate photosynthetic carbon isotope discrimination within C3 plants worldwide.” Global Ecology and Biogeography 27.9 (2018): 1056-1067.
